                        <persName xml:lang="fa">سعدی</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="en" key="work_9536">Five of the six risalahs of Sa'di.</title>
                     <note>F1a, a replacement backing for the text on the verso: note of ownership of Mir Muhammad Husain al-Ridawi al-Husaini b. Mir Abu Ja'far. undated, next to effaced seal impression. F2a: signature of David Price. Contains the preface to the Complete Works (Kulliyyat) of Sa'di compiled by Ibn BIsutun but the text only has its beginning, the first five of his six risalahs or treatises. (But not even the opening of the sixth.) Headings and punctuation in red. First page crudely illuminated.</note>
                     <incipit>Shukr u sipas ma'budi-ra jallat qudratuhu</incipit>
                     <listBibl>
                        <bibl>As for Codrington/Reade No 251.</bibl>
